# ♟️ FUTO Chess Association (FCA) Rating & Platform Software

A modern React + TypeScript platform for the **FUTO Chess Association (FCA)**. This system handles player onboarding, WhatsApp group redirection, member profiles, multi-format Elo tracking (**Blitz, Rapid, Bullet, Classical**), leaderboards, an Arbiter Console with a Lichess Arena auto-importer, and a dedicated **In Memoriam** tribute engine.

---

## 🌟 Key Features

* **FCA Onboarding ("Become an FCA Player"):** Onboarding form collecting student credentials (Full Name, Reg Number, Department, Faculty, Lichess & Chess.com handles) with auto-redirection to the official FCA WhatsApp group upon completion.
* **Multi-Format Elo Engine:** Tracks individual Elo ratings across **Blitz**, **Rapid**, **Bullet**, and **Classical** formats using standard FIDE Elo formulas.
* **Member Profiles:** Displays peak ratings, lifetime statistics, linked chess handles, and earned FCA Titles (**FCM**, **FM**, **FIM**, **FGM**).
* **Immortalized Tribute Profile (`FCA ETERNAL`):** Special database-enforced title (`FET`) reserved exclusively for **Chisom Howell**. His profile is locked from rating modifications or deletions, preserving his place in FCA history.
* **Dynamic Leaderboards:** Multi-format rankings (Blitz/Rapid/Bullet/Classical) with departmental and faculty filters.
* **Admin & Arbiter Console:**
  * **Lichess Arena Auto-Importer:** One-click import for online tournaments (e.g., 70-minute Blitz Titled Tuesdays).
  * **Unlinked Player Validation:** Cross-checks arena participants against registered FCA profiles. Games featuring unlinked Lichess handles are flagged and skipped.
  * **OTB Manual Entry:** Interface for arbiters to record physical campus matches.
* **About & Memorial Hub:** Includes club regulations, title milestone breakdowns, executive profiles, and the **Chisom Howell Tribute Page**.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Architecture

* **Frontend:** React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Lucide React (Icons)
* **Backend & Database:** Supabase (PostgreSQL, Row Level Security, Triggers)
* **API Integrations:** Lichess API (NDJSON streaming) & Chess.com Public API
* **Validation:** React Hook Form, Zod

